window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>It's a crazy day for Shanaya and work seems to be never-ending. Looking for a break, Shanaya bumps into Sameer at an unexpected moment. They have known each other for a while and their mutual attraction can be sensed from quite a distance. </p> <p>With Shanaya's love for crazy adventures, what follows is a hot and steamy session of sex in the most unexpected place. More than words, the bodies speak. </p> <p>Things could be getting quite hot in here, so <i>Call Before You Come</i>.</p>"; 
